high_descs: Turn left and go to the counter to the right of the sink
Pick up the wine glass from the sink
Turn around and go to the refrigerator on the left
Open the refrigerator door, put the wine glass on the shelf with the apple and close the door. Open the refrigerator door and take the wine glass out.
Turn left and go to the sink
Put the wine glass on the right side of the sink.

high_descs: Turn left walk forward head to the counter beside the stove
Turn right then head to the fridge
Open the fridge chill the wine glass take it out then close the fridge
Turn left then head to the sink
Put the wine glass in the sink

high_descs: Turn around and go forward to the counter adjacent to the sink.
Pick up the cup from the counter.
Turn around and go forward, then turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the cup inside, chill it, and take it out.
Turn around and step forward, then turn right and go to the sink ahead.
Put the cup inside of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold cup in the sink.
